{"tid":1891761,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"就算睇幾多動畫都好，發覺最後都係會掛住火影","createTime":"2020-02-22T05:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T18:10:50.000Z","uid":243691,"like":109,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0ab0bbe8c12eeea813e59ca75cc0b41ef09740","tid":1891761,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:31:11.000Z","msg":"由我幼稚園四五歲就開始睇火影<br />\n記得果時小李打我愛羅 鳴仔召喚文太出黎打一尾<br />\n全部都好撚熱血 即使到依家 無論火影有幾多缺點 有幾拖<br />\n我都會話火影係不能被超越既一套作品<br />\n<br />\n睇火影睇既係回憶 係情懷<br />\n你會同自己啲朋友玩火影拍手game <br />\n會扮火影跑 會討論邊個勁啲<br />\n三代係咪垃圾<br />\n係依一點上 火影係冇野取代到<br />\n<br />\n即使成日笑柒佐助鳴仔<br />\n但其實心底上大家都當左佢地係家人<br />\n不竟陪伴左大家十幾廿年<br />\n你會唔會拎自己屋企人同人比較<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒 火影未必係世界第一<br />\n但肯定係你同我心中既世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79178046a332e0c8ec12e81209df312d5affe6f9","tid":1891761,"uid":243691,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"火影世界第一呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891fd2ffe0614ee6bdcd47b871c84267873bbdad","tid":1891761,"uid":2364,"like":13,"dislike":5,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:32:01.000Z","msg":"火影教識我乜野叫柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6acdd952350089dabcaa9a685fc4bba508bcb874","tid":1891761,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:32:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1265786430114911/permalink/3733739793319550/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1265786430114911%2Fpermalink%2F3733739793319550%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAA2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=a279ad2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1265786430114911/permalink/3733739793319550/</a><br />\n呢套先係世界第一"},{"pid":"557074e38dc28968